# Amazon Review Sentiment Analysis

End-to-end NLP project for classifying Amazon reviews into positive or negative sentiment.

## Stack
Python, NLTK, Scikit-learn, FastAPI, Docker, Render

## Model
- TF-IDF features
- Logistic Regression classifier
- Binary sentiment output

## API
POST /predict  
Input: review text  
Output: sentiment label

## Deployment
- FastAPI inference service
- Dockerized application
- Deployed on Render

Demo Link:
https://sentiment-amazon-latest.onrender.com/

